{"id":203652,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/澳广-印度一游船沉没13人死亡/","date":"2011-12-29T13:03:49Z","modified":"2011-12-29T13:03:49Z","title":"澳广 | 印度一游船沉没13人死亡","content":"<div>\n<p>印度一游船沉没13人死亡</p>\n<p>印度南部泰米尔纳德邦25日有一艘游船倾覆后沉没，造成至少13人死亡，数人失踪。.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<p>2011  年 12 月 26 日</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3398034.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/decrease.gif\" alt=\"Decrease\" title=\"Decrease\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3398034.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/standard.gif\" alt=\"Standard\" title=\"Standard\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3398034.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/increase.gif\" alt=\"Increase\" title=\"Increase\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/mailto/mailto-nojs_query.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3398034.htm&#038;presname=/ra\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/email.gif\" alt=\"Email\" title=\"Email\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/printfriendly.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3398034.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/print.gif\" alt=\"Print\" title=\"Print\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3398034.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/favourite.gif\" alt=\"Favourite\" title=\"Favourite\" /></a></p>\n<p>印度南部泰米尔纳德邦25日有一艘游船倾覆后沉没，造成至少13人死亡，数人失踪。</p>\n<p>当地警方说，事故发生在距泰米尔纳德邦首府金奈58公里的一个湖中，20多名游客乘坐游船游览时遇到风浪，船只倾覆沉没，所有游客坠入水中。</p>\n<p>当地渔民从水中救起3人，并找到13具遇难者遗体。警方称目前仍在寻找失踪者，死亡人数可能上升。</p>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\